{"tid":645390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳周永康引致中朝關係惡化","createTime":"2018-04-28T05:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T11:21:00.000Z","uid":144372,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc7d7a7ba5e44315c890d171e8030409bc77633","tid":645390,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:49:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=254089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D254089&d=3B7IGMWn8NwjOBrodkRQjy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e6bc49fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D254089&h=a74e469b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=254089</a><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台】日本傳媒報道，北韓領導人金正恩的兄長金正男去年在馬來西亞被殺，可能跟前中共政治局常委周永康向金正恩洩密有關。<br />\n<br />\n日本放送協會引述一名中國官員報道，2012年八月亦即是北韓前領導人金正日逝世八個月後，當時北韓第二號人物金正恩的姑丈張成澤訪華，向時任國家主席胡錦濤表示，希望由金正男繼承權力，成為北韓最高領導人。<br />\n<br />\n周永康指使下屬將兩人的對話偷錄下來，並在2013年年初洩露給已經掌權的金正恩。同年十二月張成澤因為叛國罪被處死，周永康就在2015年因受賄和洩露國家機密等罪名被判無期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n去年二月，金正男在馬來西亞吉隆坡機場遭暗殺，報道指中方相信周永康洩密促使金正恩剷除金正男和張成澤。"},{"pid":"4e390f159fd5664d3147a8e599d2ab9b506219d1","tid":645390,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"習帝又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cef378331e96ec2c0915c3d72da9efcd126ecc","tid":645390,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e390f159fd5664d3147a8e599d2ab9b506219d1","tid":645390,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"習帝又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma